User wants a tool that will help him analyse his Java code.

User opens a terminal, starts a program that fetches his repo with Java code and analyses it.

User starts a GUI application that fetches his repo with Java code and analyses it.

User wants a tool that will create a .csv file with git information about analysed commits.

User wants to be able to manipulate multiple repositories at the same time.

User wants to define the folder for saving analyses output files and wants to pick the folder 
where the repos will be saved after analysis.
